				</simpara></listitem>
				<listitem><simpara>
					DNS TXT records are now shown via the UMC DNS module (<u:bug>25356</u:bug>).
				</simpara></listitem>
				<listitem><simpara>
					This update corrects problems with multi-edit operations as well as create and edit operations for UCS systems that have joined an existing AD domain (<u:bug>39779</u:bug>).
				</simpara></listitem>
			</itemizedlist>
